description:
**WATCH WITH CAPTIONS TO BETTER UNDERSTAND THE STORY
**A Part of this Video had to be muted because it was copyrighted**
The Jonah and the Whale story, from the Bible, in LEGO Form!!
This was a high school student project from 2013.

It was a blast taking all 2,059 pictures with our friends, and i hope you like this LEGO Stopmotion attempt, at telling the Biblical Story, Jonah and the Whale. :) Enjoy everyone!
and leave in the comments below, on how you liked it! Thank you!
